answers.answer: It is unlikely to be caused by your diabetes unless you are having much higher numbers (300+) and experiencing DKA. Davocet can cause nausea. GERD doesn't usually cause this, and I know nothing about the kidney disease. Stay hydrated and if it continues into tomorrow I would go see a doctor.
